<?php include_once($_SERVER['DOCUMENT_ROOT'] . '/assets/php/html/min/imports/importPath.php'); ?><!doctypehtml><html lang=en><meta charset=utf-8><?php include_once('global/sharedStyles.php'); ?><link href="/assets/styles/css/min/local/help/faq.min.css<?php echo $svQueryString; ?>"rel=stylesheet><title>FAQ - ShiftCodesTK</title><meta content="FAQ - ShiftCodesTK"name=title><meta content="FAQ - ShiftCodesTK"property=og:title><meta content="FAQ - ShiftCodesTK"property=twitter:title><meta content="Answers to some frequently asked questions"name=description><meta content="Answers to some frequently asked questions"property=og:description><meta content="Answers to some frequently asked questions"property=twitter:description><meta name=canonical href=https://shiftcodes.tk/help/faq><meta content=https://shiftcodes.tk/help/faq property=og:url><meta content='[{"name": "Help Center", "url": "/help/"}, {"name": "FAQ", "url": "/help/faq"}]'name=breadcrumbs id=breadcrumbs><meta content=https://shiftcodes.tk/assets/img/metadata/help/faq.png property=og:image><meta content=https://shiftcodes.tk/assets/img/metadata/help/faq.png property=twitter:image><link href=/assets/manifests/main.webmanifest rel=manifest><meta content=#f00 name=theme-color-tm id=theme_color_tm><?php include_once('global/head.php'); ?><body data-theme=main><?php include_once('global/beforeContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/main-header.php'); ?><main class=content-wrapper><header class="dropdown-panel toc"><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=icon><span class="fas fa-list-alt"></span></div><div class=string><h2 class=primary>Table of Contents</h2></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"id=table_of_contents></div></header><section class=group><header><h2>SHiFT</h2></header><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>What is SHiFT?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>SHiFT is a service created by Gearbox to reward their players with in-game loot and special events.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Do you need an account to use SHiFT?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>Yes. You can create a free account <a aria-label="Register for SHiFT (External Link)"class=themed href=https://shift.gearboxsoftware.com/registration/pre rel="external noopener"target=_blank title="Register for SHiFT (External Link)"><span class="fas fa-external-link-square-alt"aria-label="External Link"title="External Link"> </span><span class=label>here</span></a>.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>How old do you need to be to use SHiFT?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>You must be at least 18 years old to sign up for SHiFT.</div></div></section><section class=group><header><h2>ShiftCodesTK</h2></header><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Is ShiftCodesTK affiliated with Gearbox or 2K?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>Nope, ShiftCodesTK is a completely fan-made service, and is not affiliated with Gearbox Software or 2K Games in any way.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Can you create a SHiFT Code for me? Can you change the properties of a SHiFT Code? Can you give me a legendary?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>No, we have no control over the SHiFT Codes themselves, and just share the codes released by Gearbox.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Why is ShiftCodesTK not updated as soon as SHiFT Codes are posted?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>At the time of writing, ShiftCodesTK does not have access to the necessary features of the Twitter & Facebook APIs to retrieve the necessary posts and automatically parse them, as well as lacking the ability to then update our own personal pages once this information has been obtained.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Do you have any information on future titles, expansions, or events related to Borderlands?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>Nope, we have no information on anything regarding the future of Borderlands.</div></div></section><section class=group><header><h2>SHiFT Codes</h2></header><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>What are SHiFT Codes?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>SHiFT Codes are 25-character keys that grant in-game rewards.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Where are SHiFT Codes released?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>SHiFT Codes are typically released on Twitter and Facebook via official handles, but are also sometimes released during special events and livestreams.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>How often are SHiFT Codes released?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>SHiFT Codes are typically released every Friday around 10AM PST.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>Do SHiFT Codes ever expire?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>Yes, most SHiFT Codes will be issued with an Expiration Date, typically about two to three weeks after their release. However, some SHiFT Codes have and can be issued without an Expiration Date.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>How many times can a SHiFT Code be redeemed?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>SHiFT Codes can be redeemed once per account.</div></div><div class=dropdown-panel><button class=header><div class=wrapper><div class=title><div class=string><h3 class=primary>What games support SHiFT Codes?</h3></div></div><div class=indicator><span class="fas fa-chevron-right"></span></div></div></button><div class="body content-container"><p>The following titles support SHiFT Codes:<ul class=styled><li>Borderlands 2<li>Borderlands: The Pre-Sequel<li>Borderlands: Game of the Year Edition</ul><p><em>There are other titles that accept SHiFT Codes, such as Battleborn, but they are not supported on ShiftCodesTK.</em></div></div></section></main><template id=toc_entry_template><div class=section><h3><a data-internalLink=true></a></h3><ul class=styled></ul></div></template><template id=toc_entry_listitem_template><li><a data-internalLink=true></a></template><?php include_once('local/support-footer.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/afterContent.php'); ?><?php include_once('global/sharedScripts.php'); ?><script async src="/assets/scripts/min/local/help/faq.min.js<?php echo $svQueryString; ?>"></script>